{"tid":1257318,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"「代理遊戲處罰法」6月25日正式執行 韓國「代練」生意末日？","createTime":"2019-06-25T13:23:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T12:19:59.000Z","uid":75050,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7f5951ef0bc37098468e19d783ebda577dad7f85","tid":1257318,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T13:23:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://greatgame.asia/「代理遊戲處罰法」正式執行-韓國「代練」生意末/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgreatgame.asia%2F%E3%80%8C%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E8%99%95%E7%BD%B0%E6%B3%95%E3%80%8D%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%9F%B7%E8%A1%8C-%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E3%80%8C%E4%BB%A3%E7%B7%B4%E3%80%8D%E7%94%9F%E6%84%8F%E6%9C%AB%2F&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDkqdoMPUcUEfVTbHbk%2Bo2EU%3D&h=cebdc0c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://greatgame.asia/「代理遊戲處罰法」正式執行-韓國「代練」生意末/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>「代理遊戲處罰法」正式執行 韓國「代練」生意末日？</ins></strong><br />\n游雲<br />\n<br />\n於2018年韓國通過了一條名為「代理遊戲處罰法」的法案，今日6月25日終於正式執行，條例中提及了關於「代練」的部份，<strong><ins>根據法案內容所及，就是玩家之間不能以收取報酬方式，使用他人帳號幫其角色提升等級或提升排名，以及進行角色強化，將以違例論處，同時若果在「團戰」部份，與委託人進行之「決戰」部份，亦會納入非法的範圍內，違例者將會處以兩年監禁或最高2000萬韓元(約13萬港元)的罰款。</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imagizer.imageshack.com/img924/9170/XuEYYd.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimagizer.imageshack.com%2Fimg924%2F9170%2FXuEYYd.jpg%3F&h=6a3a0689&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>對戰遊戲《英雄聯盟》也是不少代練公司的重點項目</em><br />\n<br />\n這些條款主要針對是收受利益部份，若果不涉及金錢或物質是不屬於違法，<strong><ins>至於如何判定「代練」的問題，就是會依靠遊戲公司的執行部份，他們將會以登入記錄、IP位置、得勝率變化來進行密切的關注</ins></strong>，當發現有可疑的帳號，便會聯絡相關的搜查機構進行調查，希望能創造出一個公平遊戲的健康環境。"},{"pid":"adc4f376cd77320da59a43391c9724d728beb778","tid":1257318,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:45:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc757f6f56de035a912d09f50b227307d9d0929c","tid":1257318,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T16:59:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd122ccf255ed163003c4bb484d5e70e53e373ba","tid":1257318,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T22:02:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd26741c136c8a65072018b99a1db49995d643ef","tid":1257318,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T12:19:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}